   <text>
      <body>
         <div subtype="1" type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="mc027a.small.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name type="place">Winchester <choice>
                           <abbr>Tenn.</abbr>
                           <expan>Tennessee</expan>
                        </choice>
                     </name>
                     <date when="1836-08-19">August 19th 1836</date>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
               <salute>Gentlemen</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>The present is to say that we wish to know what disposition you made with the four cotton gins we sent you last December. your <choice>
                  <abbr>Recpt.</abbr>
                  <expan>Receipt</expan>
               </choice> calls for 3 @ 200$ and one at 125$</p>
            <p>We should be obliged if you write us on <choice>
                  <abbr>Recpt.</abbr>
                  <expan>Receipt</expan>
               </choice> of this whether you have sold any of the above gins as yet and whether we can receive any of the money for them this ensuing fall</p>
            <closer>
               <salute>Your Friends</salute>
               <salute>Respectfully</salute>
               <name type="person">James R. Hobbs &amp; <choice>
                     <abbr>Co.</abbr>
                     <expan>Company</expan>
                  </choice>
               </name>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name type="person">
                        <choice>
                           <abbr>Mess.</abbr>
                           <expan>Messieurs</expan>
                        </choice> Grantham &amp; Welcker</name>
                     <name type="place">Talladega <choice>
                           <abbr>Alaâ€”</abbr>
                           <expan>Alabama</expan>
                        </choice>
                     </name>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
            </closer>
            <pb n="2" facs="mc027b.small.jpg"/>
         </div>
         <div subtype="1">
            <p>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <abbr>Mess</abbr> Grantham &amp; Welker</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>Talladega <choice>
                        <abbr>Ala</abbr>
                        <expan>Alabama</expan>
                     </choice>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
               <add place="left of address">Mail }</add>
            </p>
         </div>
